headline: Interactive Brokers (IBKR) Upgraded to Buy: Here's Why
summary: Interactive Brokers (IBKR) has been upgraded to a Zacks Rank #2 (Buy), reflecting growing optimism about the company's earnings prospects. This might drive the stock higher in the near term.
